snippet.title: ASCENDANTS Rising - First Teaser
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1181780/Ascendants_Rising/
ASCENDANTS Rising is a CO-OP Action RPG that lets you create your own unique playstyle and team to explore an ever-changing Multiverse teeming with deadly enemies, formidable Boss fights, and amazing loot.
